<br>
Here are some samples:<br>
<br>
Thryft's Incinerating Strike<br>
Level 65<br>
Decrease Hitpoints by 4110<br>
Mana: 640<br>
Casting Time: 10<br>
Recast Time: 2.25<br>
Resist: Fire<br>
Resist Adjust -10<br>
Range: Melee<br>
<br>
Thryft's Thundering Blow<br>
Level 63<br>
Decrease Hitpoints by 3457<br>
Mana: 580<br>
Casting Time: 9<br>
Recast Time: 2.25<br>
Resist: Magic<br>
Range: Melee<br>
<br>
Thryft's Glacial Impalement<br>
Level 60<br>
Decrease Hitpoints by 1800<br>
Mana: 300<br>
Casting Time: 5<br>
Recast Time: 16<br>
Resist: Cold<br>
Resist Adjust -10<br>
Range: Melee<br>
<br>
Comments?<br>
<br>
-Raystonn<br>
<br>
P.S. I also think we need a big Ice nuke to go along with our big fire and magic ones.<br>
